{"summary":"With no signs that the market will rise any time soon, another round of corporate reshuffling has begun, including for those at the very top.","webName":"theblock.co","link":"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/178348\/layoffs-mount-as-october-marks-6-months-of-crypto-downturn","publishDate":"2022-10-19T13:39:14","id":6025,"type":null,"title":"Fintech layoffs mount as October marks 6 months of crypto downturn","category":["HIRING"],"content":["<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">After the Terra-Luna collapse sent crypto prices tumbling in May, many firms trimmed substantial parts of their workforce to stabilize their businesses.&nbsp;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">In June, for example, Coinbase laid off around 1,100 employees, BlockFi cut roughly 20% of its workforce, or about 170 people, and Crypto.com let go of over 260 people. The Verge later reported that this number was closer to 2,000.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Since then, many crypto firms have focused on preparing their operations to withstand a crypto winter. Like FTX, Kraken and Nexo, some have continued to hire, albeit less dramatically.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">But with no signs that the market will rise any time soon, another round of corporate reshuffling has begun, including for those at the very top. MicroStrategy chief Michael Saylor, Kraken\u2019s Jesse Powell, Genesis head Michael Moro, Sam Trabucco of Alameda Research, FTX president Brett Harrison and Celsius CEO Alex Mashinsky are all among the high-profile crypto leaders&nbsp;that have left top roles in crypto in the last few months.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">With a fresh round of job cuts underway, here is a roundup of all the job losses that have happened in crypto since April.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">April<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">May&nbsp;<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">June<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">July<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">August<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=